						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1680 (1757 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>The record is incomplete. States that Sāmavēdi Rāmayyaṅgār <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Śrīraṅga Kalyāṇa Rāmānujasvāmin, the nephew of Periya Kalyāṇa Rāmānujasvāmin succeeded the latter in the supervision of the affairs of the Daśāvatāra temple. The details of date viz., <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1680, Īśvara, Puraṭṭāśi, śu. 13, Satabhishak</hi> regularly correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1757, September 25, Sunday, ·79 ·92 See No. 561</hi> above. </p>						

						</summary>
